Package bluej.codecoverage.utils.serial

Beans for Jacoco's coverage information.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Coverage
    Represents the common elements of all code coverage elements.
    CoverageBridge
    Extracts needed information from Jacoco's coverage, and turns it into a serializable representation.
    CoverageBridgeTest  
    CoverageClass
    Serializable representation of IClassCoverage This class can be used by BlueJ extensions that are using a different ClassLoader through Serialization.
    CoverageCounter
    Serializable representation of ICounter This class can be used by BlueJ extensions that are using a different ClassLoader through Serialization.
    CoverageLine
    Serializable representation of ILine This class can be used by BlueJ extensions that are using a different ClassLoader through Serialization.
    CoverageMethod
    Represents Code coverage for a method.
    CoveragePackage
    Represents coverage information for an entire package, with an individual CoverageClass for each class in the package.
    CoverageTestCase  
    CoverageTestCase.TestBuilder  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CoverageBranch
    Joins Coverage information for a branch with icons to indicate coverage.
    CoverageCounterValue
    Serializable representation of CounterValue.
    CoverageType
    Joins Coverage information for Java Object's with their respective icon.
